title: # 507 - Jared Freid & ME
itunes:title: # 507 - Jared Freid & ME
description:
Today, I sit down with comedian, Jared Freid. We talk about tour food, family dynamics, his parents retirement community, his new special, dating, and much more! 

 

Check out his podcast “The J Train Podcast” here: https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/the-jtrain-podcast/id672249013 

 

Check out his new special “Jared Freid: Socially Distanced... Of Course” on YouTube here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Q7dxL8hPdbk 

 

Follow Jared 

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jaredfreid 

Twitter: https://twitter.com/jtrain56
